36:57.883 --> 36:59.818
<i>♪ I can feel it ♪</i>

36:59.818 --> 37:02.654
<i>♪ I can feel the power ♪</i>

37:16.935 --> 37:20.105
Hey, there's no ticket.

37:20.105 --> 37:23.041
It's not printing a ticket.

37:23.041 --> 37:25.877
Oh, I forgot you worked here.

37:25.877 --> 37:29.047
Slashing tires isn't,
like, part of the job, is it?

37:29.047 --> 37:31.016
I told you that wasn't me.

37:31.016 --> 37:32.918
Okay,
can you open this thing?

37:32.918 --> 37:34.820
We're late for a movie.

37:42.661 --> 37:46.465
You do look nice, your skin.

37:46.465 --> 37:48.166
We're seeing a movie.
You want to come?

37:48.166 --> 37:52.838
Um, I'm working.

37:52.838 --> 37:54.540
Have fun.

37:54.540 --> 37:56.975
We will. Thanks.

38:00.211 --> 38:01.580
News.

38:01.580 --> 38:02.781
News, now.

38:02.781 --> 38:04.249
No, no, no, no, no.
Don't touch that.

38:04.249 --> 38:05.351
- News.
- No, no.

38:05.351 --> 38:06.652
It's not that kind of TV.

38:06.652 --> 38:08.019
- News, now.
- No, Danny, stop.

38:08.019 --> 38:09.087
Danny.
Danny, stop.

38:16.328 --> 38:19.130
Ow, Danny, you hit me.

38:19.130 --> 38:20.399
Remember, it's not okay to hit.

38:20.399 --> 38:23.835
No hitting.
No hitting.

38:57.302 --> 38:59.538
- Hi, hi.
- Stay down.

39:08.046 --> 39:10.048
Hello?

39:12.150 --> 39:13.919
Hello?

39:33.338 --> 39:35.340
Late for a movie?

39:43.482 --> 39:45.083
Ugh, shit.

39:47.453 --> 39:49.387
I need to check something.

39:49.387 --> 39:51.022
Stay here, okay?

39:53.391 --> 39:55.627
I'm gonna lock the door.

39:55.627 --> 39:57.796
I'll be back in five minutes.

40:00.766 --> 40:01.867
Five minutes.

40:22.754 --> 40:24.456
Phoebe?

40:37.102 --> 40:39.370
Phoebe?

40:43.308 --> 40:45.110
Oh, my God.

40:45.110 --> 40:47.245
There's no way he said that.

40:47.245 --> 40:49.147
I'm serious, he did.

40:49.147 --> 40:50.849
Oh, shit.

40:50.849 --> 40:52.884
Aren't you late for a movie?

40:52.884 --> 40:55.220
It's just the trailers.

40:55.220 --> 40:57.288
We're seeing a movie?

40:57.288 --> 40:58.757
Oh, my God.

40:58.757 --> 41:00.258
No more weed for you, girl.

41:00.258 --> 41:01.860
No.

42:39.758 --> 42:41.593
Jerry?

42:55.340 --> 42:57.208
Danny.

42:57.208 --> 42:59.377
As of 9:22 p.m. Thursday,

42:59.377 --> 43:03.214
<i>state officials reported
the flame was 14% contained,</i>

43:03.214 --> 43:06.184
<i>but 6,452 acres burned.</i>

43:06.184 --> 43:09.220
<i>The fire's prompted evacuation
orders for nearly seven--</i>

44:16.654 --> 44:18.156
Danny?

44:24.462 --> 44:25.997
Danny?

44:28.867 --> 44:30.501
Danny, where are you?

44:30.501 --> 44:32.037
Danny?

44:33.204 --> 44:34.973
Danny?

44:39.044 --> 44:40.712
Danny?

44:40.712 --> 44:42.280
Where are you?

44:43.381 --> 44:44.983
Where are you?

44:44.983 --> 44:46.617
Danny?

44:51.056 --> 44:53.258
Danny?

45:02.734 --> 45:04.202
Danny?

45:25.256 --> 45:31.129
Danny!

45:40.005 --> 45:41.739
Come on, come on, come on.

45:41.739 --> 45:43.441
Dad, Dad, it's me.

45:43.441 --> 45:44.575
You have
to call me back, please.

45:44.575 --> 45:46.711
I--I can't find Danny.

45:46.711 --> 45:48.113
I left him here
for five minutes.

45:48.113 --> 45:49.580
And I locked the door,
I swear to God.

45:49.580 --> 45:50.615
And I can't find him.

45:50.615 --> 45:52.517
You have
to call me back, please.

45:52.517 --> 45:54.252
Please just call me back.

46:26.417 --> 46:27.585
Are you okay?

46:27.585 --> 46:29.354
Oh, Danny, look at me.
Where were you?

46:36.794 --> 46:38.396
It was here.

46:43.935 --> 46:46.504
Wait, what are you doing here?

46:46.504 --> 46:48.239
I heard you.

46:48.239 --> 46:49.207
You what?

46:49.207 --> 46:51.642
I heard you scream his name.

46:51.642 --> 46:53.644
From where?

46:53.644 --> 46:55.813
My house.

46:55.813 --> 46:58.549
How did you get here so fast?

46:58.549 --> 47:01.652
I don't know.
I th--

47:01.652 --> 47:03.454
I think I ran.

47:15.133 --> 47:18.536
You heard me too.

47:18.536 --> 47:21.172
You heard me scream his name.

47:21.172 --> 47:22.407
Yeah.

47:22.407 --> 47:24.142
Why?

47:24.142 --> 47:26.912
Because you didn't scream.

47:26.912 --> 47:29.847
You howled.

47:39.690 --> 47:42.260
Oh, you scared me.

47:42.260 --> 47:43.861
Can I help you with something?

47:43.861 --> 47:45.363
Yeah.

47:45.363 --> 47:46.998
You can give this to her.

47:48.699 --> 47:50.635
Tell her it's for her wall.

50:01.099 --> 50:02.267
It kills every night.

50:02.267 --> 50:04.402
<i>And now it's killing for you.</i>

50:05.470 --> 50:06.837
Slow down!

50:06.837 --> 50:08.206
Are we not trying
to save someone's life?

50:08.206 --> 50:10.108
You do want to know
something, don't you?

50:10.108 --> 50:11.376
It's still here!

50:11.376 --> 50:12.977
You're practically doing
my job for me.

50:12.977 --> 50:14.011
Guys.
